name: Nevermore
description:
Quoth the raven, "Nevermore"

This model is good in bringing in life things that existed nowhere and nevermore... and better should stay there... but if you insist...

Merge of one private anime model and Monster Diffusion.

Can also do usual anime / drawing stuff, just sometimes with extra quirks.
